727351f-a.text:
Maspeth Ave., south side, between 53rd and 54th Streets, showing the site upon which one stood the William H. Furman mansion. This individual owned most of the surrounding land and homes in which many
members of his family lived.
March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
